			<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>In short your domain should be&#8230;</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span data-type="circle"   class="qode_icon_shortcode fa-stack q_font_awsome_icon_stack fa-1x  q_icon_animation" style=" "><i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-base fa-stack-2x" style="color: #22bbd3;"></i><i class="qode_icon_font_awesome fa fa-thumbs-up qode_icon_element fa-stack-1x" style="" ></i></span> <strong>Catchy</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span data-type="circle"   class="qode_icon_shortcode fa-stack q_font_awsome_icon_stack fa-1x  q_icon_animation" style=" "><i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-base fa-stack-2x" style="color: #22bbd3;"></i><i class="qode_icon_font_awesome fa fa-thumbs-up qode_icon_element fa-stack-1x" style="" ></i></span> <strong>Unique</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span data-type="circle"   class="qode_icon_shortcode fa-stack q_font_awsome_icon_stack fa-1x  q_icon_animation" style=" "><i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-base fa-stack-2x" style="color: #22bbd3;"></i><i class="qode_icon_font_awesome fa fa-thumbs-up qode_icon_element fa-stack-1x" style="" ></i></span> <strong>Easy to remember</strong></p>

