			<h3 style="text-align: center; font-size: 30px; text-transform: capitalize;"><strong>The Last Step. </strong></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center; font-size: 30px; text-transform: capitalize;"><strong>Setting Up Your WordPress Website &amp; Making It Look Professional!</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>The boring stuff is nearly done!</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">So you have purchased your domain name and hosting and now it&#8217;s time to make your website function. In just a few minutes your site will come alive.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">The first thing you need to do is install WordPress. Sounds hard, but it&#8217;s not! Easy as pie!</p>

